title: Dow Movers: MCD, INTC - Nasdaq.com
text: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of Intel Corp ( INTC  ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.7%. Year to date, Intel Corp registers a 1.8% gain.      And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is McDonald's Corp ( MCD  ), trading down 0.1%. McDonald's Corp is showing a gain of 22.1% looking at the year to date performance.  makeArticleAd();    Two other components making moves today are Pfizer ( PFE  ), trading flat on the day, and Dow ( DOW  ), trading up 1.6% on the day.
